title: Fan art: Polymer clay figures and drawings

embed.description: Mostly League of legends fan art 🐸 Here are some of my creations 🐸 Summoner name: grönnfrosk 🐸 Role: sup. Rank: gold 1 atm 🐸 Server: EU west 🐸

body: Hello :) Making figures is my hobby. Which champion should be the next one i make? :D

replies.body: Love the blitz one! Nice work on some of those tougher ones like Rengar and Gnar too :D
awesome rammus, the blitz with the spring arms is my fav :-p
Oh my gosh!! These are so cute, your cat cuddling with Teemo melted my heart <3

Ahh!! These are so cute ;~;  
kindred would be interesting, or illaoi
